{
  "video_id": "7hWUhEA6hxk",
  "title": "Epigenetics: David Shenk at TEDxLakeGeneva",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13635.0,
      "end_time": 17552.0,
      "text": "I am middle-aged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17552.0,
      "end_time": 20679.0,
      "text": "as you can see."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20679.0,
      "end_time": 22105.0,
      "text": "What that means is that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22105.0,
      "end_time": 26077.0,
      "text": "day by day, I become a lot more reliant and trusting"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26077.0,
      "end_time": 28554.0,
      "text": "of machines like this"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28554.0,
      "end_time": 31941.0,
      "text": "than I am of this machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31941.0,
      "end_time": 34677.0,
      "text": "Like some of you, I suspect, I&#39;m increasingly aware"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34677.0,
      "end_time": 39085.0,
      "text": "of the frailties of the human body and brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39085.0,
      "end_time": 43455.0,
      "text": "And I look around at this technological revolution taking place."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43455.0,
      "end_time": 49073.0,
      "text": "And I kind of want to apply this same ingenuity to the human body"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 49073.0,
      "end_time": 51787.0,
      "text": "to upgrade myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51787.0,
      "end_time": 55959.0,
      "text": "After all, if we&#39;ve gone from this"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55959.0,
      "end_time": 57716.0,
      "text": "to this"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 57716.0,
      "end_time": 60193.0,
      "text": "in my lifetime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60193.0,
      "end_time": 63501.0,
      "text": "why can&#39;t we go from this"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 63501.0,
      "end_time": 65200.0,
      "text": "to this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65200.0,
      "end_time": 69879.0,
      "text": "Why can&#39;t I, why can&#39;t we all be stronger, smarter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 69879.0,
      "end_time": 74857.0,
      "text": "faster, longer lasting?"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 74857.0,
      "end_time": 78233.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve all seen great new inventions that are aimed at doing just that;"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 78233.0,
      "end_time": 80398.0,
      "text": "upgrading the human body."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 80398.0,
      "end_time": 84369.0,
      "text": "High-tech replacements for our hands and arms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 84369.0,
      "end_time": 89380.0,
      "text": "our knees and legs, our eyes and ears,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 89380.0,
      "end_time": 90574.0,
      "text": "even our brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 90574.0,
      "end_time": 97448.0,
      "text": "Google has an ambition to connect the brain directly to the internet;"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 97448.0,
      "end_time": 100910.0,
      "text": "no typing or speaking required."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 100910.0,
      "end_time": 104468.0,
      "text": "Think about that for a second, kind of creepy, kind of cool?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 104468.0,
      "end_time": 108678.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sure it will happen if Google is going after it."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 108678.0,
      "end_time": 115959.0,
      "text": "The main reason that we fantasize about these biological, these bionic upgrades"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 115959.0,
      "end_time": 121219.0,
      "text": "is that our own biological upgrades happen so infrequently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 121219.0,
      "end_time": 123746.0,
      "text": "at least that&#39;s what we were told in school, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 123746.0,
      "end_time": 125849.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s what we were taught:"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 125849.0,
      "end_time": 129502.0,
      "text": "Once upon a time we evolved from this"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 129502.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131855.0,
      "text": "to this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 131855.0,
      "end_time": 136839.0,
      "text": "to this, to this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 136839.0,
      "end_time": 137858.0,
      "text": "to this."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 137858.0,
      "end_time": 141647.0,
      "text": "And now, we are who we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 141647.0,
      "end_time": 144467.0,
      "text": "This is Darwin&#39;s famous natural selection."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 144467.0,
      "end_time": 148963.0,
      "text": "It is thought to be the one and only,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 148963.0,
      "end_time": 152439.0,
      "text": "very slow upgrade mechanism that we have."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 152439.0,
      "end_time": 156541.0,
      "text": "And what we were told was, we&#39;re stuck in place"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 156541.0,
      "end_time": 161682.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ll stay just like this until a random genetic mutation happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 161682.0,
      "end_time": 166778.0,
      "text": "and spreads throughout the entire species."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 166778.0,
      "end_time": 172214.0,
      "text": "For most of the grand time scale of human existence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 172214.0,
      "end_time": 173970.0,
      "text": "we stay the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 173970.0,
      "end_time": 176280.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what we were taught."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 176280.0,
      "end_time": 178670.0,
      "text": "But that turns out not to be the case."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 178670.0,
      "end_time": 181835.0,
      "text": "If you look closely at science from the last few decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 181835.0,
      "end_time": 184592.0,
      "text": "a very different lesson emerges."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 184592.0,
      "end_time": 188653.0,
      "text": "Humans are self-upgradeable."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 188653.0,
      "end_time": 191805.0,
      "text": "We are designed to upgrade on our own."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 191805.0,
      "end_time": 195789.0,
      "text": "Not just every few hundred thousand years, but all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 195789.0,
      "end_time": 198476.0,
      "text": "We have a genetic operating system"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 198476.0,
      "end_time": 209864.0,
      "text": "whose function it is to constantly adapt to external conditions and needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 209864.0,
      "end_time": 213968.0,
      "text": "Imagine if Apple held an event and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 213968.0,
      "end_time": 216581.0,
      "text": "here&#39;s your new iPhone 6"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 216581.0,
      "end_time": 218964.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re really gonna want to buy this one"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 218964.0,
      "end_time": 222170.0,
      "text": "because you&#39;ll never have to buy another one."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 222170.0,
      "end_time": 226565.0,
      "text": "Next year this iPhone 6 will turn into an iPhone 7."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 226565.0,
      "end_time": 231376.0,
      "text": "The year after that, it will turn into an iPhone 8,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 231376.0,
      "end_time": 232980.0,
      "text": "not just the software,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 232980.0,
      "end_time": 236824.0,
      "text": "the hardware itself will transform right in your hand"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 236824.0,
      "end_time": 240223.0,
      "text": "and into what you need it to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 240223.0,
      "end_time": 244341.0,
      "text": "So, the screen will become bigger or smaller depending on what you need,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 244341.0,
      "end_time": 250217.0,
      "text": "the glass will become more flexible or more rigid depending on what you need,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 250217.0,
      "end_time": 255087.0,
      "text": "the case will become harder or softer or more grippy or smoother"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 255087.0,
      "end_time": 258733.0,
      "text": "depending on what you need."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 258733.0,
      "end_time": 262117.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what human beings do."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 262117.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264661.0,
      "text": "We constantly adapt"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 264661.0,
      "end_time": 269736.0,
      "text": "to our external conditions and needs using not one, but four"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 269736.0,
      "end_time": 273088.0,
      "text": "different biological upgrade mechanisms."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 273088.0,
      "end_time": 276591.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve already talked about natural selection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 276591.0,
      "end_time": 279374.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s the slowest by far,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 279374.0,
      "end_time": 282425.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s the only one we don&#39;t get to see in our own lifetime."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 282425.0,
      "end_time": 284697.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s talk about the other three."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 284697.0,
      "end_time": 288771.0,
      "text": "First upgrade mechanism is homeostasis."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 288771.0,
      "end_time": 290823.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a biochemical system"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 290823.0,
      "end_time": 294319.0,
      "text": "that allows the body to adapt constantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 294319.0,
      "end_time": 297222.0,
      "text": "second to second, minute to minute, hour to hour,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 297222.0,
      "end_time": 300307.0,
      "text": "to environmental changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 300307.0,
      "end_time": 303317.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s an example of homeostasis?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 303317.0,
      "end_time": 307081.0,
      "text": "I am in my warm New York City apartment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 307081.0,
      "end_time": 309656.0,
      "text": "I decide to go outside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 309656.0,
      "end_time": 310771.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s freezing cold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 310771.0,
      "end_time": 313753.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m in the middle of a freezing cold blizzard all of a sudden."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 313753.0,
      "end_time": 317415.0,
      "text": "Immediately, my hypothalamus sends signals"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 317415.0,
      "end_time": 321447.0,
      "text": "to constrict the blood vessels close to my skin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 321447.0,
      "end_time": 325009.0,
      "text": "it activates my skeletal muscles to shiver and generate warmth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 325009.0,
      "end_time": 328960.0,
      "text": "the hair on my skin raises up to trap warm air,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 328960.0,
      "end_time": 333530.0,
      "text": "glands secrete adrenaline and thyroxine to increase my metabolic rate."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 333530.0,
      "end_time": 337694.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not even aware of it, but my body has just immediately"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 337694.0,
      "end_time": 340877.0,
      "text": "self-adjusted to a new environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 340877.0,
      "end_time": 344076.0,
      "text": "it is instantly upgraded to deal with the cold."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 344076.0,
      "end_time": 347237.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s homeostasis, upgrade mechanism number one."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 347237.0,
      "end_time": 349757.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m outside"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 349757.0,
      "end_time": 354044.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m actually on my way to my son&#39;s school a few blocks away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 354044.0,
      "end_time": 357309.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s in the fifth grade and he&#39;s learning to play the violin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 357309.0,
      "end_time": 364408.0,
      "text": "and today I get to hear his first orchestra concert."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 364408.0,
      "end_time": 367556.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 367556.0,
      "end_time": 371237.0,
      "text": "You do too."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 371237.0,
      "end_time": 383428.0,
      "text": "(Music continues)"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 383428.0,
      "end_time": 386791.0,
      "text": "I think if my fifth grade orchestra had been anywhere near that hip,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 386791.0,
      "end_time": 390380.0,
      "text": "my life would have gone in a completely different direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 390380.0,
      "end_time": 395453.0,
      "text": "So what&#39;s going on with my son as he is learning to play the violin?"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 395453.0,
      "end_time": 400737.0,
      "text": "He is experiencing and enjoying upgrade mechanism number two:"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 400737.0,
      "end_time": 401966.0,
      "text": "neuroplasticity."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 401966.0,
      "end_time": 405671.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve all heard of neuroplasticity; it&#39;s the brain&#39;s way of becoming smarter"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 405671.0,
      "end_time": 409334.0,
      "text": "by building connections between neurons"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 409334.0,
      "end_time": 411737.0,
      "text": "and strengthening those connections."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 411737.0,
      "end_time": 414771.0,
      "text": "And even though neurons are obviously very, very small,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 414771.0,
      "end_time": 418222.0,
      "text": "all these connections actually physically change"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 418222.0,
      "end_time": 420859.0,
      "text": "the shape of your brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 420859.0,
      "end_time": 422929.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t emphasize this enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 422929.0,
      "end_time": 428489.0,
      "text": "this involves every single skill you have ever learned or will ever learn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 428489.0,
      "end_time": 431037.0,
      "text": "and we know it from peer-reviewed science."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 431037.0,
      "end_time": 436738.0,
      "text": "Using MRI scans, neuroscientists have seen the subtle physical changes"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 436738.0,
      "end_time": 440727.0,
      "text": "in the brains of musicians learning a new instrument,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 440727.0,
      "end_time": 444064.0,
      "text": "cab drivers learning the geography of a different city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 444064.0,
      "end_time": 447982.0,
      "text": "meditation practitioners training their brain in a new way"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 447982.0,
      "end_time": 454182.0,
      "text": "and all sorts of athletes."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 454182.0,
      "end_time": 459261.0,
      "text": "The brain is built to adapt to your needs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 459261.0,
      "end_time": 462596.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s what it&#39;s designed to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 462596.0,
      "end_time": 468131.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s upgrade mechanism number two."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 468131.0,
      "end_time": 472627.0,
      "text": "So, we&#39;ve got a problem here, what about this interval?"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 472627.0,
      "end_time": 475228.0,
      "text": "We seem to have every time scale covered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 475228.0,
      "end_time": 477496.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve got seconds, minutes, hours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 477496.0,
      "end_time": 481024.0,
      "text": "all the way up to millions and millions of years covered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 481024.0,
      "end_time": 483924.0,
      "text": "all these three mechanisms are working so well together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 483924.0,
      "end_time": 486145.0,
      "text": "but what about this interval here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 486145.0,
      "end_time": 488277.0,
      "text": "Generation to generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 488277.0,
      "end_time": 490549.0,
      "text": "This is where the story gets a little strange"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 490549.0,
      "end_time": 492070.0,
      "text": "and, to me, very interesting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 492070.0,
      "end_time": 496231.0,
      "text": "because for a long time, scientists were quite convinced"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 496231.0,
      "end_time": 499073.0,
      "text": "there was no biological mechanism for adaptation"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 499073.0,
      "end_time": 501146.0,
      "text": "from generation to generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 501146.0,
      "end_time": 504369.0,
      "text": "We have culture, we have education, we have events like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 504369.0,
      "end_time": 508330.0,
      "text": "these things can do a tremendous amount in that time period,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 508330.0,
      "end_time": 513171.0,
      "text": "but not these three biological mechanisms; natural selection is way too slow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 513171.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515240.00000000006,
      "text": "you can have a random genetic mutation"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 515240.0,
      "end_time": 519316.0,
      "text": "but you can&#39;t have it spread that quickly through the human species."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 519316.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521541.00000000006,
      "text": "Neuroplasticity also doesn&#39;t apply here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 521541.00000000006,
      "end_time": 527068.0,
      "text": "my son can change his brain dramatically in his lifetime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 527068.0,
      "end_time": 531318.0,
      "text": "but he can&#39;t change the brain of his future son"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 531318.0,
      "end_time": 534390.0,
      "text": "or grandson."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 534390.0,
      "end_time": 536162.0,
      "text": "Or can he?"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 536162.0,
      "end_time": 541344.0,
      "text": "Because it turns out that there is a very peculiar biological mechanism"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 541344.0,
      "end_time": 545915.0,
      "text": "that fits right in this interval of generation to generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 545915.0,
      "end_time": 549139.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called epigenetic inheritance."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 549139.0,
      "end_time": 551980.0,
      "text": "Epigenetic inheritance, by the way, was just discovered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 551980.0,
      "end_time": 556158.0,
      "text": "so if you haven&#39;t heard of it, forgive yourself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 556158.0,
      "end_time": 557612.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a brand new discovery."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 557612.0,
      "end_time": 560556.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve known of epigenetics, but epigenetic inheritance"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 560556.0,
      "end_time": 563067.0,
      "text": "is really brand new to science."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 563067.0,
      "end_time": 564612.0,
      "text": "And what is it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 564612.0,
      "end_time": 568780.0,
      "text": "It is the understanding that anything in our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 568780.0,
      "end_time": 572971.0,
      "text": "anything we eat, breathe, our moods, behaviors and so forth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 572971.0,
      "end_time": 577942.0,
      "text": "affects our genes and that some of those effects on the genes"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 577942.0,
      "end_time": 581700.0,
      "text": "can actually get passed down to our children and grandchildren."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 581700.0,
      "end_time": 584142.0,
      "text": "Now, this is going to sound nuts to you guys"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 584142.0,
      "end_time": 587894.0,
      "text": "because we&#39;re all raised to think about genes in a certain way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 587894.0,
      "end_time": 590266.0,
      "text": "which is that you can&#39;t change your genes."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 590266.0,
      "end_time": 592412.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s true, you can&#39;t change your genes."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 592412.0,
      "end_time": 596336.0,
      "text": "The most fundamental thing about DNA is that it&#39;s stable."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 596336.0,
      "end_time": 600433.0,
      "text": "50% of your DNA is a perfect replica from your mother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 600433.0,
      "end_time": 605248.0,
      "text": "the other 50% is a perfect replica from your father,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 605248.0,
      "end_time": 609333.0,
      "text": "but DNA comes wrapped up in a protective package of proteins"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 609333.0,
      "end_time": 611511.0,
      "text": "called the epigenome."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 611511.0,
      "end_time": 615926.0,
      "text": "&quot;Epi&quot; is Latin for &quot;outside,&quot; so epigenome means outside the genome."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 615926.0,
      "end_time": 618964.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s an illustration of what the epigenome looks like"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 618964.0,
      "end_time": 622044.0,
      "text": "at a magnification of about 1 million."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 622044.0,
      "end_time": 625997.0,
      "text": "You can see the double helix strands of DNA wrapped around"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 625997.0,
      "end_time": 629806.0,
      "text": "the epigenetic proteins."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 629806.0,
      "end_time": 632307.0,
      "text": "Now, these proteins not only protect DNA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 632307.0,
      "end_time": 634248.0,
      "text": "they also influence gene expression,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 634248.0,
      "end_time": 639025.0,
      "text": "which means they tell genes when to turn on and off."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 639025.0,
      "end_time": 642882.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;ve known for a long time that our lifestyle can influence our genes"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 642882.0,
      "end_time": 645197.0,
      "text": "through epigenetics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 645197.0,
      "end_time": 647163.0,
      "text": "what scientists just discovered"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 647163.0,
      "end_time": 650309.0,
      "text": "through many studies now in plants and animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 650309.0,
      "end_time": 654963.0,
      "text": "is that some of those effects can get passed down to our children."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 654963.0,
      "end_time": 656658.0,
      "text": "And very recently we&#39;ve seen"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 656658.0,
      "end_time": 659643.0,
      "text": "some really amazing population studies in humans"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 659643.0,
      "end_time": 662769.0,
      "text": "that suggest that the exact same thing is going on in us."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 662769.0,
      "end_time": 666819.0,
      "text": "Now, admittedly, we do not have the perfect examples yet in human beings."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 666819.0,
      "end_time": 670509.0,
      "text": "Why is that? We can&#39;t manipulate human breeding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 670509.0,
      "end_time": 672050.0,
      "text": "we can&#39;t clone humans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 672050.0,
      "end_time": 675625.0,
      "text": "we can&#39;t do with humans what we would ordinarily need to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 675625.0,
      "end_time": 676865.0,
      "text": "to do these studies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 676865.0,
      "end_time": 680161.0,
      "text": "but the scientists who study this are quite convinced"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 680161.0,
      "end_time": 685314.0,
      "text": "that epigenetic inheritance is real and ubiquitous."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 685314.0,
      "end_time": 687841.0,
      "text": "So that brings us back to this marvelous chart."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 687841.0,
      "end_time": 693493.0,
      "text": "Now it&#39;s complete, we see our four upgrade mechanisms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 693493.0,
      "end_time": 696233.0,
      "text": "each perfectly complementing one another"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 696233.0,
      "end_time": 699834.0,
      "text": "and covering the entire time scale of existence."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 699834.0,
      "end_time": 702065.0,
      "text": "And, by the way, these ideas are not mine."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 702065.0,
      "end_time": 705099.0,
      "text": "I, of course, am learning them from scientists."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 705099.0,
      "end_time": 708566.0,
      "text": "Here are two scientists I wanted to give credit to and thanks to"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 708566.0,
      "end_time": 711765.0,
      "text": "for doing an early version of this time scale chart"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 711765.0,
      "end_time": 714038.0,
      "text": "and putting it all together."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 714038.0,
      "end_time": 716518.0,
      "text": "Why am I so obsessed with this chart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 716518.0,
      "end_time": 718583.0,
      "text": "and I keep coming back to it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 718583.0,
      "end_time": 721419.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just a dry list of words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 721419.0,
      "end_time": 725441.0,
      "text": "but I don&#39;t think I&#39;ve ever seen"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 725441.0,
      "end_time": 731252.0,
      "text": "an illustration that better demonstrates how humans are built for adaptivity."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 731252.0,
      "end_time": 736542.0,
      "text": "We are designed to upgrade on our own, we are self-upgradeable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 736542.0,
      "end_time": 740062.0,
      "text": "we are designed to change from moment to moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 740062.0,
      "end_time": 742612.0,
      "text": "from month to month, and year to year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 742612.0,
      "end_time": 747151.0,
      "text": "from generation to generation, and over hundreds of thousands"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 747151.0,
      "end_time": 751090.0,
      "text": "and millions of years."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 751090.0,
      "end_time": 755509.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t just inherit our biology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 755509.0,
      "end_time": 758264.0,
      "text": "we also impact our biology."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 758264.0,
      "end_time": 761134.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s an amazing opportunity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 761134.0,
      "end_time": 764132.0,
      "text": "and also a very serious burden."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 764132.0,
      "end_time": 768001.0,
      "text": "So what can human beings transform themselves into?"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 768001.0,
      "end_time": 770148.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s easy for me to stand up here"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 770148.0,
      "end_time": 773562.0,
      "text": "and obsess about my own middle-aged problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 773562.0,
      "end_time": 778413.0,
      "text": "my creaky bones, and fantasize about some new high-tech solution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 778413.0,
      "end_time": 780816.0,
      "text": "and we know those solutions will come."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 780816.0,
      "end_time": 785105.0,
      "text": "But then I think about this chart, and I think about my son"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 785105.0,
      "end_time": 788432.0,
      "text": "and how he&#39;s gonna transform himself"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 788432.0,
      "end_time": 790739.0,
      "text": "over the course of his life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 790739.0,
      "end_time": 795087.0,
      "text": "and some of those changes will get passed on to his children"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 795087.0,
      "end_time": 797092.0,
      "text": "and to their children."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 797092.0,
      "end_time": 800333.0,
      "text": "And thinking about that, I am filled with a hope"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 800333.0,
      "end_time": 805924.0,
      "text": "and a sense of awe for this very, very old technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 805924.0,
      "end_time": 807825.0,
      "text": "inside each one of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 807825.0,
      "end_time": 810014.0,
      "text": "Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 810014.0,
      "end_time": 820014.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}